{"tid":1287010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好同佢傾，無人代表到群眾！ 佢回應到訴求群眾自然會散！","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:59:53.000Z","uid":219007,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9586e10756c8530f053275d99a744695543e61f3","tid":1287010,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"無大台有好處亦有壞處<br />\n<br />\n而佢搵唔到群眾既代表同佢談判就係無大台既好處<br />\n<br />\n因為任何人都不能夠直接代表群眾，群眾亦唔能夠確保代表者有冇出賣自己。<br />\n<br />\n只要林鄭回應左群眾訴求，群眾自然就散。<br />\n<br />\n我地就係要佢搵唔到人同佢談判。"},{"pid":"e7186a18768a4ecbcc7036f7e4dbff44126b91fc","tid":1287010,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1314dbb7d4523e299c95afd60e45c572dccc890","tid":1287010,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭約見　大學學生會：如允不追究反送中示威者等兩條件，願考慮對話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n即出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事"},{"pid":"4d4199ac81395e6596d02c28d664658a4bb82566","tid":1287010,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"應該約見晒200萬人嚟傾先有用"},{"pid":"c0d3a8e5421acff20fe9b4f7cc5f0576f4a4933c","tid":1287010,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:53:23.00